    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "surrender feels like the only thing that makes sense... but what does that even mean? like if i just stop fighting, i'm just still here. i'm still stuck in this body and this life that's so broken. is there even a way to actually find rest? like real rest, where it finally just stops?",
